Implemented the fixes in place and wrote `./ADDRESS_SUMMARY.md`.

Changes made:
- Forwarded `security.environmentVariableRedaction.allowed` through `loadCliConfig` as `allowedEnvironmentVariables`.
- Added exactly-once prepared-command cleanup guards in the shell child-process and PTY setup paths so cleanup runs if setup throws after sandbox preparation.

Verification:
- `npm run typecheck --workspace @google/gemini-cli-core` passed.
- `npm run typecheck --workspace @google/gemini-cli` passed.

I did not edit test files because the allowed edit set and instructions prohibit touching tests.
